676
01:07:42,180 --> 01:07:42,920
 da pravo nas

677
01:07:42,920 --> 01:07:45,440
 osigura ostanak

678
01:07:45,440 --> 01:07:46,360
 u takvom nekakvom

679
01:07:46,360 --> 01:07:46,840
